      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_button",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我最爱之人，是瓷器店的老板。",
      "tone": "大声回答",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bao_button",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他最奇的相貌，是鼻子很大，而且是个酒糟鼻子。",
      "tone": "理直气壮",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duanyu",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我最快乐的地方，是在一口枯井的烂泥之中。",
      "tone": "温柔深情",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duanyu",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她……她是我这一生最爱的女子。",
      "tone": "温柔坚定",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duanyu",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她容貌极美，我怎也看不厌。",
      "tone": "深情自然",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zongzan",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我最快乐的地方，是在洞房花烛夜，和新娘子一同在喜堂里。",
      "tone": "张扬自信",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_murongfu",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有。",
      "tone": "冷然",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_murongfu",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我没有最爱的人。",
      "tone": "冷然",
      "chapter": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuzhu",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "黑暗的冰窖。",
